creator: Nordnet Bank AB
descriptionHtml:
Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device. Download the app today and make your money grow.

We provide all tools, services and products you need to follow the stock markets and trade wherever you are. Create your own tailor-made watch lists, see the latest development of your portfolio and check the status of your pending orders. The app is free to download and use.

More smart features
- Login to the app using Mobile Bank ID, username and password or biometric login (Fingerprint)
- Search, inspect, buy and sell equities or mutual funds
- Check your pending or complete orders
- See your positions and the value of your portfolio. Check your portfolio or instrument performance for different time periods on the graph.
- Create your own watch lists. Watchlist sync automatically between the app and new nordnet.se.
- Get the latest financial news about the market and your positions

The app is free
See current prices for our services and products that you can use here: https://www.nordnet.se/tjanster/prislista/oversikt.html

When you download our app you accept that we are using cookies. This is how we are using cookies: https://www.nordnet.se/mux/web/info/cookies.html

Feedback
We are using your feedback to continuously improve the app. Please rate the app and send us your thoughts and ideas in comments.

Security
All logged in traffic between the app and our systems is encrypted. Don’t leave your phone without first logging out. If you have been inactive for more than 60 minutes you will be logged out automatically.

Contact Information

Nordnet Bank AB
Box 30099
104 25 Stockholm

Tel. +46 8-506 330 00
Organisational number: 516406-0021
E-mail: info@nordnet.se

descriptionShort: Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
No need to leave the account page to make a deposit or view account specific transactions anymore. We've added an action button at the bottom of the account screen to make account specific actions and information accessible with fewer clicks.

You also get streaming of latest trades on the instrument and order screens in this version.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Please welcome our new discover screen! When you go to the search tab, before you start searching you will see the latest articles about the stock market from our blog. You will also find today's winners and losers on this screen. We show 5 instruments on each card, for more results simply tap on the card. Stay tuned, there’s more to come on the discover screen!

We've also updated the watchlists where in addition to today's development we now display development for 3 months and 1 year.

descriptionHtml:
Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device. Download the app today and make your money grow.

We provide all tools, services and products you need to follow the stock markets and trade wherever you are. Create your own tailor-made watch lists, see the latest development of your portfolio and check the status of your pending orders. The app is free to download and use.

More smart features
- Login to the app using Mobile Bank ID, username and password or biometric login (Fingerprint)
- Search, inspect, buy and sell equities or mutual funds
- Check your pending or complete orders

- Create your own watch lists. Watchlist sync automatically between the app and new nordnet.se.

descriptionShort: Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device.
title: Nordnet

creator: Nordnet Bank AB
descriptionHtml:
Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device. Download the app today and make your money grow.

We provide all tools, services and products you need to follow the stock markets and trade wherever you are. Create your own tailor-made watch lists, see the latest development of your portfolio and check the status of your pending orders. The app is free to download and use.

More smart features
- Login to the app using Mobile Bank ID, username and password or biometric login (Fingerprint)
- Search, inspect, buy and sell equities or mutual funds
- Check your pending or complete orders
- See your positions and the value of your portfolio. Check your portfolio or instrument performance for different time periods on the graph.
- Create your own watch lists. Watchlist sync automatically between the app and new nordnet.se.
- Get the latest financial news about the market and your positions

The app is free

Take your savings to the next level with the Nordnet App. Buy and sell stocks, funds, ETF:s and other financial instruments, directly on your phone.

Oversee your investments with notifications about transaction, buy orders and dividends. Your investments are always close - just like it should be.

The app is of course free to use.

Become a customer in three minutes.
It is easy to get going. Create an account directly in the app with Mobilt BankID. Use swish or bank transfer to start trading.

Get started from 0 SEK.
Trade stocks for free on the Stockholm Stock Exchange, up to 80 000 SEK during your first six months. Activate the offer by changing to the Mini courtage on your desktop and register a Shareville account.

Automatic monthly savings.
Free guiding to build a custom made fund saving. Choose risk, savings horizon and and amount - we assist you with the rest.

Shareville: The largest network for savings and investments in the Nordics.
Find inspiration and real time trading advice by proven successful investors through our popular network Shareville - for free.

Large offer of stocks and funds.
Choose between thousands of securities. Get inspired by the stocks other investors own, or choose funds based on your saving targets: sustainable, low fee or high dividend.

Get inspired.
Tips, inspiration and in-depth articles in the app helps you to invest wisely.

Move your securities free of charge.
Get better control of your investments by moving your securities to Nordnet in a few simple steps.

Real time price alerts supports quick action.
Receive push notifications when securities you follow reach a level of your choice.

About Nordnet.
We are a leading pan-Nordic digital platform for savings and investments with more than 1,5 million users in Sweden, Finland, Norway and Denmark.

We challenge traditional structures through innovation, simplicity and transparency and provide private savers with the same information, tools and services as professional investors.

Welcome to Nordnet.
descriptionShort: Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device.

creator: Nordnet Bank AB
descriptionHtml:
Buy and sell everything. Anywhere.
Take your savings to the next level with the Nordnet App. Buy and sell stocks, funds, ETF:s and other financial instruments, directly on your phone.

Oversee your investments with notifications about transaction, buy orders and dividends. Your investments are always close - just like it should be.

The app is of course free to use.

Become a customer in three minutes.
It is easy to get going. Create an account directly in the app with Mobilt BankID. Use swish or bank transfer to start trading.

Get started from 0 SEK.
Trade stocks for free on the Stockholm Stock Exchange, up to 80 000 SEK during your first six months. Activate the offer by changing to the Mini courtage on your desktop and register a Shareville account.

Automatic monthly savings.
Free guiding to build a custom made fund saving. Choose risk, savings horizon and and amount - we assist you with the rest.

Shareville: The largest network for savings and investments in the Nordics.
Find inspiration and real time trading advice by proven successful investors through our popular network Shareville - for free.

Large offer of stocks and funds.
Choose between thousands of securities. Get inspired by the stocks other investors own, or choose funds based on your saving targets: sustainable, low fee or high dividend.

Get inspired.
Tips, inspiration and in-depth articles in the app helps you to invest wisely.

Move your securities free of charge.
Get better control of your investments by moving your securities to Nordnet in a few simple steps.

Real time price alerts supports quick action.
Receive push notifications when securities you follow reach a level of your choice.

About Nordnet.
We are a leading pan-Nordic digital platform for savings and investments with more than 1,5 million users in Sweden, Finland, Norway and Denmark.

We challenge traditional structures through innovation, simplicity and transparency and provide private savers with the same information, tools and services as professional investors.

Welcome to Nordnet.

- What are your largest investments? The analysis tab will give you the answer
- How many funds do you own? The analysis tab will give you the answer
- Are you too heavy in a stock? The analysis tab will give you the answer

Take your savings to the next level with the Nordnet App. Buy and sell stocks, funds, ETF:s and other financial instruments, directly on your phone.

Oversee your investments with notifications about transaction, buy orders and dividends. Your investments are always close - just like it should be.

The app is of course free to use.

Become a customer in three minutes.
It is easy to get going. Create an account directly in the app with Mobilt BankID. Use swish or bank transfer to start trading.

Get started from 0 SEK.
Trade stocks for free on the Stockholm Stock Exchange, up to 80 000 SEK during your first six months. Activate the offer by changing to the Mini courtage on your desktop and register a Shareville account.

Automatic monthly savings.
Free guiding to build a custom made fund saving. Choose risk, savings horizon and and amount - we assist you with the rest.

Shareville: The largest network for savings and investments in the Nordics.
Find inspiration and real time trading advice by proven successful investors through our popular network Shareville - for free.

Large offer of stocks and funds.
Choose between thousands of securities. Get inspired by the stocks other investors own, or choose funds based on your saving targets: sustainable, low fee or high dividend.

Get inspired.
Tips, inspiration and in-depth articles in the app helps you to invest wisely.

Move your securities free of charge.
Get better control of your investments by moving your securities to Nordnet in a few simple steps.

Real time price alerts supports quick action.
Receive push notifications when securities you follow reach a level of your choice.

About Nordnet.
We are a leading pan-Nordic digital platform for savings and investments with more than 1,5 million users in Sweden, Finland, Norway and Denmark.

We challenge traditional structures through innovation, simplicity and transparency and provide private savers with the same information, tools and services as professional investors.

Welcome to Nordnet.
descriptionShort: Trade stocks, mutual funds and other equities instantly via your mobile device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Tightened some screws, replaced a few parts that were beginning to show signs of wear. Mostly improvements under the hood.

title: Nordnet

descriptionHtml:
Buy and sell everything. Anywhere.

The app is of course free to use.

Get started from 0 SEK.

Free guiding to build a custom made fund saving. Choose risk, savings horizon and and amount - we assist you with the rest.

Shareville: The largest network for savings and investments in the Nordics.

Get inspired.
Tips, inspiration and in-depth articles in the app helps you to invest wisely.

Move your securities free of charge.
Get better control of your investments by moving your securities to Nordnet in a few simple steps.

Real time price alerts supports quick action.
Receive push notifications when securities you follow reach a level of your choice.

title: Nordnet

creator: Nordnet Bank AB
descriptionHtml:
With Nordnet's award-winning app, investing in stocks, funds, and ETFs is easier than ever. In the app you can track your progress and what is happening on the stock market. It's completely free to download and use the app.

- We offer trading in stocks, funds, and other securities at low fees on several of the world's largest exchanges.
- Discover new investments through top and theme lists, articles, and current campaigns.
- See discussions about investing and specific stocks and funds from our users.
- Follow your holdings and the stock market's development in real-time.


GET STARTED IN THREE MINUTES

Create an account directly in the app. Deposit your money easily and secure to start trading and investing.

LOW FEES FOR TRADING AND INVESTING

Always low fees regardless of how little or much you trade. Choose the commission class that fits your trading.

AUTOMATIC MONTHLY INVESTING

Save automatically each month in funds. Get help choosing a fund plan that suits you.

WIDE RANGE OF STOCKS AND FUNDS

Choose from thousands of stocks and funds on multiple exchanges around the world. Get inspired by other investors' stock holdings or choose funds based on your savings goals: sustainable, low fees, or highest returns.

REAL TIME PRICE ALERTS

Get a push notification when your watched stocks and other securities reach the level you have set.

WATCHLISTS

Find your next investment through our watchlists. Choose industries that interest you and then get lists of instruments within those themes. Use it as inspiration to find new investments or to keep an eye on exciting companies. You can also create your own watchlists.

LISTEN AND READ REPORTS WITH QUARTR

In partnership with Quartr, you can easily keep track of your favorite stocks by listening to company presentations during quarterly and annual reports. You can also download reports and presentations in text format.

INTERACTIVE GRAPHS

Compare your investments with relevant indexes and see how you perform over time. See features for more advanced investors, such as trading volume and candlesticks.

SAFE AND EASY

Log in with Touch-ID or Face-ID. Hide your balance if you, for example, want to log in in public environments.

ABOUT NORDNET

We are a leading Nordic digital broker for savings and investments with over 1.5 million customers in Sweden, Finland, Norway, and Denmark.


Through innovation, simplicity, and transparency, we challenge traditional structures and give private savers access to the same information, tools, and services as professional investors. Welcome to Nordnet.

descriptionShort: Invest and trade, follow the stock market, see your holdings and read news.
title: Nordnet: Stocks & Funds

creator: Nordnet Bank AB
descriptionHtml:
With Nordnet's award-winning app, investing in stocks, funds, and ETFs is easier than ever. In the app you can track your progress and what is happening on the stock market. It's completely free to download and use the app.

• We offer trading in stocks, funds, and other securities at low fees on several of the world's largest exchanges.
• Discover new investments through top and theme lists, articles, and current campaigns.
• See discussions about investing and specific stocks and funds from our users.
• Follow your holdings and the stock market's development in real-time.


Get started in three minutes.


Create an account directly in the app. Deposit your money easily and secure to start trading and investing.


Low fees for trading and investing.


Always low fees regardless of how little or much you trade. Choose the commission class that fits your trading.


Automatic monthly investing.


Save automatically each month in funds. Get help choosing a fund plan that suits you.


Wide range of stocks and funds.


Choose from thousands of stocks and funds on multiple exchanges around the world. Get inspired by other investors' stock holdings or choose funds based on your savings goals: sustainable, low fees, or highest returns.


Real time price alerts.


Get a push notification when your watched stocks and other securities reach the level you have set.


Watchlists.


Find your next investment through our watchlists. Choose industries that interest you and then get lists of instruments within those themes. Use it as inspiration to find new investments or to keep an eye on exciting companies. You can also create your own watchlists.


Listen and read reports with Quartr.


In partnership with Quartr, you can easily keep track of your favorite stocks by listening to company presentations during quarterly and annual reports. You can also download reports and presentations in text format.


Interactive graphs.


Compare your investments with relevant indexes and see how you perform over time. See features for more advanced investors, such as trading volume and candlesticks.


Safe and easy.


Log in with Touch-ID or Face-ID. Hide your balance if you, for example, want to log in in public environments.

In these times of political hardening.
We are going softer.

The experience is sharper than ever before.
